      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and shows its age through typical wear and tear. The exterior has some noticeable paint fading on the hood and roof, along with a few scuffs and small dings around the bumpers. Inside, the cabin remains functional, though the upholstery shows significant wear and there are some minor stains on the carpeting. While the car is currently drivable, it will likely require some mechanical attention soon, such as a suspension tune-up and addressing a minor oil seep, to ensure continued reliability.",
