    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for your next big adventure? I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape, runs smoothly, and has been well-loved. It's perfect for daily commutes or weekend getaways! I\u2019d love for it to go to a great new home, so come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 29900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
