      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This FD3S chassis remains a benchmark in balanced handling, featuring a near-perfect weight distribution and aluminum double-wishbone suspension. Under the hood, the 13B-REW sequential twin-turbocharged rotary engine delivers linear power, with the secondary Hitachi HT12 turbocharger engaging smoothly at 4,500 RPM. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise 5-speed manual transmission and a Torsen limited-slip differential. Recent service includes a cooling system overhaul with a high-capacity radiator and a refresh of the complex vacuum-actuated turbo control system. Compression remains within factory specifications, ensuring the integrity of the apex seals. While the exterior shows honest patina from spirited use, the mechanical fundamentals are dialed in for the driving enthusiast.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used vehicle in good condition. Mechanically sound. Clean title. Minor cosmetic wear. Well-maintained.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offering a well-maintained vehicle that perfectly captures the balance of performance and reliability. The exterior retains a high-gloss finish, accented by clean body lines; while there are a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper consistent with careful daily use, the overall curb appeal remains strong. Step inside to a smoke-free cabin where the upholstery has been preserved with regular conditioning. The driver\u2019s seat shows only light softening of the bolster, and the dashboard remains free of any cracks or sun damage. Every electronic component, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system, operates flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine runs quietly and pulls strongly, backed by a complete folder of service records. Recent maintenance includes a fresh fluid service and a cooling system flush. The tires offer deep tread for the seasons ahead, and the suspension remains tight and responsive. This car is a dependable, honest example of the model, ready for its next owner to drive home with confidence.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
